{"tid":2118152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌認為極端情況才實施「禁足令」","createTime":"2020-07-21T09:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T09:59:26.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66db87b5c6451dd36d878c356ccf32ad50cbe4f3","tid":2118152,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"許樹昌認為極端情況才實施「禁足令」<br />\n2020-07-21 HKT 17:11<br />\n<br />\n&quot;消息指，行政會議明天舉行特別會議，討論強制戴口罩的規定，擴展至所有室內公眾場所。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;至於未來會否有需要實施「禁足令」，許樹昌表示，政府上周開始加強社交距離措施，包括禁止食肆晚6朝5堂食等，要一至兩周的時間觀察措施的效用，視乎確診數字在今個星期後段會否有下降跡象，特別是來歷不明的個案。他說，若措施有效就只須延長現有措施，但如果到今個星期後段，每日確診數字仍接近三位數字，就有需要「加辣」，例如要求食肆全日不准做堂食。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539062-20200721.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539062-20200721.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=0a9b7218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539062-20200721.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=639ca456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539062-20200721.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">確診數字距離三位數字越來越遠，「禁足令」應該不會實施，大家仍可繼續出街玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"81d40c0a2a604f58f123a0ec600279bc7aec9dc0","tid":2118152,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"起碼要4位數字先叫極端啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a13019d23c6cd3b0d218543a51c705fb62bf0cf","tid":2118152,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"係咪傻撚左,如果佢真係出到禁足佢下一步就係&quot;你班港豬想返工?咁要去政府到攪健康碼&quot;<br />\n<br />\n唔撚好比藉口佢行第一步"},{"pid":"0478fed898610199b6d01d284429f0275e82ce76","tid":2118152,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}